# Google Identity Services (GIS) OAuth 2.0 client ID.
# Required for silent token refresh — without this, Drive access tokens expire after
# 1 hour and cannot be renewed automatically (browser blocks the popup fallback).
# Get this from: Google Cloud Console > APIs & Services > Credentials > OAuth 2.0 Client IDs
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=""

